	  drawing code. Almost completely rewrote paint_rle(), and moved it to
	  Image_buffer8
	* imagewin/scale.cc, imagewin/scale.h: Slightly improved Point and
	  Interlaced scalers.
	* msvcstuff/msvc_kludges.h: Tweak

